                                    Online shop

Our project is about online shop. The name of our project is BSAD. We create a website in the type of online store. It will be similar to the current well-known olx.kz. But the difference is we have things that are not used, and new. Here you can also sort things by criteria, find what you need. Only in our offer you will be able to put stars and write reviews, and therefore themselves will choose proven things for good reviews. We have a huge range of products, such as clothes, accessories,(bags, jewellery), cosmetics, and so on.  
Our main aim is to give opportunity to quickly find things for people, who have not time to go to the shopping. 
Our vision.
We want make our online shop useful, so everyone can use it. In the 1 year we hope that we will end our project and will gather about 1000 users. 

